Wayne Blair https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayne_Blair 0 Wayne Blair (born 28 November 1971) is an Indigenous Australian writer, actor and director, seen most recently on both sides of the camera in Redfern Now. He is also the director of the highly successful feature film The Sapphires.
